* Create a virtual environment with: python3 -m venv venv
* Go into it using: source /venv/bin/activate
* Install dependencies using: pip install -r requirements.txt

* Use daytrading_loading.py to load our data.
* Use cleaning.py to clean our data.
* Merge any data at this stage.
* Finally use parquet_converter.py to convert the CSV to a parquet file.
